Class TheGuardianDataSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unipd.dei.eis.data.sources.DataSource<TheGuardianDataEntity,Object>
      • it.unipd.dei.eis.data.sources.TheGuardianDataSource

  • public class TheGuardianDataSource
extends DataSource<TheGuardianDataEntity,Object>
    TheGuardianDataSource is the data source for The Guardian records. It contains the data source logic.
